quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  29,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  29,1,alif l- meem
  29,2,"kya logon ne yeh samajh rakha hai ke woh bas itna kehnay par chore diye jayen ge ke"" hum imaan laaye"" aur un ko aazmaaya nah jaye ga ?"
  29,3,halan ke hum unn sab logon ki azmaish kar chuke hain jo inn se pehlay guzray hain Allah ko to zaroor yeh dekhna hai ke sachey kon hain aur jhutay kon
  29,4,aur kya woh log jo burii harkatein kar rahay hain yeh samjhay baithy hain ke woh hum se baazi le jayen ge? bara ghalat hukum hai jo woh laga rahay hain
  29,5,"jo koi Allah se milnay ki tawaqqa rakhta ho ( ussay maloom hona chahiye ke ) Allah ka muqarrar kya howa waqt anay hi wala hai, aur Allah sab kuch sُnta aur jaanta hai"
  29,6,"jo shakhs bhi Mujahida karega apne hi bhallay ke liye kere ga, Allah yaqeenan duniya Jahan walon se be niaz hai"
  29,7,aur jo log imaan layein ge aur naik aamaal karen ge unn ki buraiyan hum un se door kar den ge aur inhen unn ke behtareen aamaal ki jaza den ge
  29,8,"hum ne ensaan ko hadaayat ki hai ke apne walidain ke sath naik sulooq kere lekin agar woh tujh par zor dalain ke to mere sath kisi aisay ( mabood ) ko shareek tehra-ay jisay to ( mere shareek ki hesiyat se ) nahi jaanta to un ki itaat nah kar meri hi taraf tum sab ko palat kar aana hai, phir mein tum ko bta dun ga ke tum kya karte rahay ho"
  29,9,aur jo log imaan laaye hon ge aur jinhon ne naik aamaal kiye hon ge unn ko hum zaroor salheen mein daakhil karen ge
  29,10,"logon mein se koi aisa hai jo kehta hai ke hum imaan laaye Allah par magar jab woh Allah ke maamla mein sataya gaya to is ne logon ki daali hui azmaish ko Allah ke azaab ki terhan samajh liya ab agar tairay rab ki taraf se fatah o nusrat aa gayi to yahi shakhs kahe ga ke"" hum to tumahray sath thay"" kya duniya walon ke dilon ka haal Allah ko bakhoobi maloom nahi hai ?"
  29,11,aur Allah ko to zaroor yeh dekhna hi hai ke imaan laane walay kon hain aur munafiq kon
  29,12,"yeh kafir log imaan laane walon se kehte hain ke tum hamaray tareeqay ki pairwi karo aur tumhari khataon ko hum apne ooper le len ge halaank unn ki khataon mein se kuch bhi woh apne oopar lainay walay nahi hain, woh qatan jhoot kehte hain"
  29,13,haan zaroor woh apne boojh bhi uthayen ge aur apne bojhon ke sath bohat se dosray boojh bhi aur qayamat ke roz yaqeenan un se inn aftarapardaziyunki bazprs ho gi jo woh karte rahay hain
  29,14,hum ne Nooh ko is ki qoum ki taraf bheja aur woh pachaas kam aik hazaar baras unn ke darmain raha aakhir-kaar unn logon ko tufaan ne aa ghaira is haal mein ke woh zalim thay
  29,15,phir Nooh ko aur kashti walon ko hum ne bacha liya aur ussay duniya walon ke liye aik nishaan Ibrat bana kar rakh diya
  29,16,"aur ibrahim ko bheja jabkay uss ne apni qoum se kaha"" Allah ki bandagi karo aur uss se daro yeh tumahray liye behtar hai agar tum jano"
  29,17,"tum Allah ko chore kar jinhein پوج rahay ho woh to mehez buut hain aur tum aik jhoot ghurr rahay ho Dur haqeeqat Allah ke siwa jin ki tum parastish karte ho woh tumhe koi rizaq bhi dainay ka ikhtiyar nahi rakhtay Allah se rizaq mango aur usi ki bandagi karo aur is ka shukar ada karo, isi ki taraf tum پلٹائے jaane walay ho"
  29,18,"aur agar tum jutlatay ho to tum se pehlay bohat si qoumain jhutla chuki hain, aur rasool par saaf saaf pegham pouncha dainay ke siwa koi zmmh daari nahi hai """
  29,19,"kya inn logon ne kabhi dekha hi nahi hai ke Allah kis terhan Khalq ki ibtida karta hai, phir uss ka iada karta hai? yaqeenan yeh ( iada to ) Allah ke liye aasaan tar hai"
  29,20,"un se kaho ke zameen mein chalo phiro aur dekho ke uss ne kis terhan Khalq ki ibtida ki hai, phir Allah baar deegar bhi zindagi bakhshay ga yaqeenan Allah har cheez par Qadir hai"
  29,21,"jisay chahay saza day aur jis par chahay reham farmaiye, usi ki taraf tum phairay jaane walay ho"
  29,22,"tum nah zameen mein aajiz karne walay ho nah aasman mein, aur Allah se bachanay wala koi sarparast aur madad gaar tumahray liye nahi hai"
  29,23,jin logon ne Allah ki ayaat ka aur is se mulaqaat ka inkaar kya hai woh meri rehmat se mayoos ho chuke hain aur un ke liye dard naak saza hai
  29,24,"phir uss ki qoum ka jawab iss ke siwa kuch nah tha ke unhon ne kaha"" qatal kar do isay ya jala daalo iss ko"" aakhir-kaar Allah ne usay aag se bacha liya, yaqeenan is mein nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo imaan laane walay hain"
  29,25,"aur uss ne kaha"" tum ne duniya ki zindagi mein to Allah ko chore kar buton ko apne darmain mohabbat ka zareya bana liya hai magar qayamat ke roz tum aik doosray ka inkaar aur aik doosray par laanat karo ge aur aag tumhara thikana ho gi aur koi tumhara madad gaar nah ho ga """
  29,26,"uss waqt loot ne uss ko maana aur ibrahim ne kaha mein apne rab ki taraf hijrat karta hon, woh zabardast hai aur hakeem hai"
  29,27,"aur hum ne usay ishaq aur yaqoob ( jaisi aulaad ) inayat farmai aur is ki nasal mein nabuwat aur kitaab rakh di, aur usay duniya mein uss ka ajar ataa kya aur akhirat mein woh yaqeenan salheen mein se ho ga"
  29,28,"aur hum ne loot ko bheja jabkay uss ne apni qoum se kaha"" tum to woh fehash kaam karte ho jo tum se pehlay duniya walon mein se kisi ne nahi kya hai"
  29,29,"kya tumhara haal yeh hai ke Mardon ke paas jatay ho, aur rehzani karte ho aur apni mjlson mein buray kaam karte ho ?"" phir koi jawab is ki qoum ke paas is ke siwa nah tha ke unhon ne kaha"" le aa Allah ka azaab agar to schcha hai """
  29,30,"loot ne kaha"" ae mere rab, inn mufsid logon ke muqablay mein meri madad farma """
  29,31,"aur jab hamaray farstadaybrahim ke paas basharat le kar puhanche to unhon ne uss se kaha"" hum iss bastii ke logon ko halaak karne walay hain, is ke log sakht zalim ho chuke hain """
  29,32,"ibrahim ne kaha"" wahan to loot mojood hai"" unhon ne kaha"" hum khoob jantay hain ke wahan kon kon hai hum ussay, aur is ki biwi ke siwa is ke baqi ghar walon ko bacha len ge"" is ki biwi peechay reh jaane walon mein se thi"
  29,33,"frastday loot ke paas puhanche to un ki aamad par woh sakht pareshan aur dil tang howa onhon ne kaha"" nah daro aur nah ranj karo hum tumhe aur tumahray ghar walon ko bacha len ge, siwaye tumhari biwi ke jo peechay reh jaane walon mein se hai"
  29,34,"hum is bastii ke logon par aasman se azaab nazil karne walay hain uss fisq ki badolat jo yeh karte rahay hain """
  29,35,aur hum ne uss bastii ki aik khُli nishani chore di hai unn logon ke liye jo aqal se kaam letay hain
  29,36,"aur mudin ki taraf hum ne unn ke bhai Shoiab ko bheja uss ne kaha"" ae meri qoum ke logo, Allah ki bandagi karo aur rozِ aakhir ke umeed waar raho aur zameen mein mufsid ban kar zyadtyan nah karte phiro """
  29,37,magar unhon ne usay jhutla diya aakhir-kaar aik sakht zalzalay ne inhen aa liya aur woh apne gharon mein parre ke parre reh gay
  29,38,"aur Aad o smod ko hum ne halaak kya, tum woh maqamat dekh chuke ho jahan woh rehtay thay unn ke aamaal ko shetan ne unn ke liye khushnuma bana diya aur inhen raah e raast se bur-ghashta kar diya halaank woh hosh gosh rakhtay thay"
  29,39,aur qaroon o firaon o Haman ko hum ne halaak kya moose unn ke paas bayyanaat le kar aaya magar unhon ne zameen mein apni barayi ka zeam kya halaank woh Sabqat le jaane walay nah thay
  29,40,"aakhir-kaar har aik ko hum ne is ke gunah mein pakra, phir un mein se kisi par hum ne pathrao karne wali howa bhaije, aur kisi ko aik zabardast dhamakay ne aa liya, aur kisi ko hum ne zameen mein dhassa diya, aur kisi ko ghark kar diya Allah unn par zulm karne wala nah tha, magar woh khud hi apne oopar zulm kar rahay thay"
  29,41,jin logon ne Allah ko chore kar doosray sarparast bana liye hain unn ki misaal makri jaisi hai jo apna aik ghar banati hai aur sab gharon se ziyada kamzor ghar makri ka ghar hi hota hai kash yeh log ilm rakhtay
  29,42,yeh log Allah ko chore kar jis cheez ko bhi pukarte hain Allah usay khoob jaanta hai aur wohi zabardast aur hakeem hai
  29,43,"yeh misalein hum logon ki fehmayesh ke liye dete hain, magar un ko wohi log samajte hain jo ilm rakhnay walay hain"
  29,44,"Allah ne asmano aur zameen ko barhaq peda kya hai, Dur haqeeqat iss mein aik nishani hai ehley imaan ke liye"
  29,45,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) talawat karo is kitaab ki jo tumhari taraf wahi ke zareya se bhaije gayi hai aur namaz qaim karo, yaqeenan namaz fehash aur buray kamon se rokti hai aur Allah ka zikar is se bhi ziyada barri cheez hai Allah jaanta hai jo kuch tum log karte ho"
  29,46,"aur ahal kitaab se behas nah karo magar umdah tareeqa se, siwaye unn logon ke jo unn mein se zalim hon, aur unn se kaho ke"" hum imaan laaye hain uss cheez par bhi jo hamari taraf bhaije gayi hai aur uss cheez par bhi jo tumhari taraf bhaije gayi thi, hamara khuda aur tumhara khuda aik hi hai aur hum usi ke mُslm ( farmaa bardaar ) hain """
  29,47,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) hum ne isi terhan tumhari taraf kitaab nazil ki hai, is liye woh log jin ko hum ne pehlay kitaab di thi woh is par imaan laatay hain, aur inn logon mein se bhi bohat se is par imaan laa rahay hain, aur hamari ayaat ka inkaar sirf kafir hi karte hain"
  29,48,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) tum is se pehlay koi kitaab nahi parhte thay aur nah apne haath se likhte thay, agar aisa hota to baatil parast log shak mein par satke thay"
  29,49,"darasal yeh roshan nishanain hain unn logon ke dilon mein jinhein ilm bakhsha gaya hai, aur hamari ayaat ka inkaar nahi karte magar woh jo zalim hain"
  29,50,"yeh log kehte hain ke"" kyun nah utari gayi is shakhs par nishanain iss ke rab ki taraf se ?"" kaho,"" nishanain to Allah ke paas hain aur mein sirf khabardaar karne wala hon khol khol kar """
  29,51,aur kya inn logon ke liye yeh ( nishani ) kaafi nahi hai ke hum ne tum par kitaab nazil ki jo aِnhin parh kar sُnayi jati hai? Dur haqeeqat iss mein rehmat hai aur nasiyaat hai unn logon ke liye jo imaan laatay hain
  29,52,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) kaho ke"" mere aur tumahray darmain Allah gawahi ke liye kaafi hai woh asmano aur zameen mein sab kuch jaanta hai jo log baatil ko mantay hain aur Allah se kufar karte hain wohi khasaray mein rehne walay hain """
  29,53,"yeh log tum se azaab jaldi laane ka mutalba karte hain agar aik waqt muqarrar nah kar diya gaya hota to un par azaab aa chuka hota aur yaqeenan ( apne waqt par ) woh aa kar rahay ga achanak, is haal mein ke inhen khabar bhi nah ho gi"
  29,54,"yeh tum se azaab jaldi laane ka mutalba karte hain, halaank jahannum un kafiroon ko ghairay mein le chuki hai"
  29,55,( aur inhen pata chalay ga ) uss roz jabkay azaab inhen ooper se bhi dhaank le ga aur paon ke neechay se bhi aur kahe ga ke ab chako maza un krtoton ka jo tum karte thay
  29,56,"ae mere Bandoo jo imaan laaye ho, meri zameen wasee hai, pas tum meri bandagi baja lao"
  29,57,"har mutnaqas ko mout ka maza chakhna hai, phir tum sab hamari taraf hi palta kar laaye jao ge"
  29,58,"jo log imaan laaye hain aur jinhon ne naik amal kiye hain un ko hum jannat ki buland o baala imaarton mein rakhen ge jin ke neechay nehrein behti hon gi, wahan woh hamesha rahen ge, kya hi umdah ajar hai amal karne walon ke liye"
  29,59,unn logon ke liye jinhon ne sabr kya hai aur jo apne rab par bharosa karte hain
  29,60,"kitney hi janwar hain jo apna rizaq uthaye nahi phirtay, Allah unn ko rizaq deta hai aur tumhara Razaq bhi wohi hai, woh sab kuch sُnta aur jaanta hai"
  29,61,"agar tum inn logon se pucho ke zameen aur asmano ko kis ne peda kya hai aur chaand aur sooraj ko kis ne maskhar kar rakha hai to zaroor kahin ge ke Allah ne, phir yeh kidhar se dhoka kha rahay hain ?"
  29,62,"Allah hi hai jo apne bundon mein se jis ka chahta hai rizaq kushadah karta hai aur jis ka chahta hai tang karta hai, yaqeenan Allah har cheez ka jan-nay wala hai"
  29,63,"aur agar tum un se pucho kis ne aasman se pani barsaya aur iss ke zareya se murda pari hui zameen ko jِla uthaya to woh zaroor kahin ge Allah ne kaho,Alhamdo Lillahہ, magar aksar log samajte nahi hain"
  29,64,"aur yeh duniya ki zindagi kuch nahi hai magar aik khail aur dil ka behlawa asal zindagi ka ghar to daar akhirat hai, kash yeh log jantay"
  29,65,"jab yeh log kashti par sawaar hotay hain to apne deen ko Allah ke liye khalis kar ke uss se dua mangte hain, phir jab woh aِnhin bacha kar khushki par le aata hai to yakayak yeh shirk karne lagtay hain"
  29,66,"taakay Allah ki di hui nijaat par is ka kufran Nemat karen aur ( hayaat duniya ke ) mazay lotin acha, anqareeb aِnhin maloom ho jaye ga"
  29,67,kya yeh dekhte nahi hain ke hum ne aik par aman haram bana diya hai halaank inn ke gird o paish log uchak liye jatay hain? kya phir bhi yeh log baatil ko mantay hain aur Allah ki Nemat ka kufran karte hain ?
  29,68,uss shakhs se bara zalim kon ho ga jo Allah par jhoot bandhay ya haq kojhutla-ay jab ke woh is ke samnay aa chuka ho? kya aisay kafiroon ka thikana jahannum hi nahi hai ?
  29,69,"jo log hamari khatir Mujahida karen ge inhen hum apne rastay deikhein ge, aur yaqeenan Allah naiko karon hi ke sath hai"
